      "function_name": "headlessBrowser",
      "description": "Web browser engine \u2014 navigate any URL, search the web, submit forms, and run autonomous AI agent tasks. Actions: 'navigate' (fetch and render any URL \u2014 returns page title, headings, links, images, forms, emails, phones, text content, and full visual HTML preview), 'search' (web search via DuckDuckGo \u2014 returns list of results with title, URL, snippet), 'submit_form' (submit a form on a page with field data), 'agent_task' (autonomous multi-step AI browser agent that plans and executes web tasks \u2014 uses LLM credits). Send { action: 'navigate'|'search'|'submit_form'|'agent_task', url, query, form_action, form_method, form_data, task, start_url }. PREFER navigate + search for simple tasks (no LLM credits). Use agent_task only for complex multi-step automation."
